  'canvas.toolbar.diagramGenerationImageContext':
    '[Reference material (from the user-uploaded image)]\nThe following is text, terms, relationships and structural information actually extracted from the user-uploaded image(s). Treat it as the PRIMARY source of material:\n- The 2~4 aspect headings and the 1~2 key nouns under each aspect should preferentially come from vocabulary/concepts that appear in this material;\n- Only when an aspect is not covered by the material, or when the material does not provide enough to fill the key nouns for that aspect, may you supplement with your own common-sense knowledge — minimally and only as needed;\n- Do NOT invent people or events that are absent from the material and unrelated to its topic;\n- Still strictly follow the above "2~4 items / each with 1~2 【key nouns】 + 「connector」 + Form A (『verb』+『object』) OR Form B (no 『』)" output format. Do not copy the raw material into the output, and do not add a separate quoted block.\n\n**Final format checklist (review each item; rewrite if any fails):**\n  (1) **2~4 items**, starting with "1." "2." "3." "4." etc.;\n  (2) immediately after the number, exactly one 「connectorA」 followed by the aspect heading;\n  (3) each item contains **1~2** 【key nouns】; each 【key noun】 MUST be preceded by one 「connectorB」;\n  (4) the part after each 【key noun】 is EITHER Form A (**two** `『…』` — first verb, second object) OR Form B (**no** `『…』` at all). The "single `『…』`" malformed shape is FORBIDDEN;\n  (5) across all key nouns, roughly HALF use Form A and HALF use Form B (Form A for nouns that deserve elaboration, Form B for nouns merely mentioned);\n  (6) **the TOTAL length is STRICTLY between 700 and 800 words** (counting all 「」 and 『』 content). Under 700 → expand details / add another Form-A noun; over 800 → prune or merge. Output outside the 700~800 range is unacceptable and must be rewritten;\n  (7) **Every `「connectorA」` and every `「connectorB」` must contain a real 1~3 word connector; Form-A `『verb』` and `『object』` must both be filled with real content**. Empty 「」, empty 『』, or filler words like "...", "input relation", "to be filled", "TBD" make the whole response unacceptable — rewrite it;\n  (8) before emitting, mentally count: does this line have 1~2 【】? does each 【】 have either 2 『』 or no 『』 (never just 1)? are all connectors filled with real content (no empty 「」)? does the total word count land within 700~800? only emit once everything is verified correct.\n\nMaterial:\n{imageContext}',
